item.title: CVE-2023-22377|2024-08-02T10:07:06.571Z -- fujitsu%20limited -- tsclinical%20define.xml%20generator%20and%20tsclinical%20metadata%20desktop%20tools
item.description: Improper restriction of XML external entity reference (XXE) vulnerability exists in tsClinical Define.xml Generator all versions (v1.0.0 to v1.4.0) and tsClinical Metadata Desktop Tools Version 1.0.3 to Version 1.1.0. If this vulnerability is exploited, an attacker may obtain an arbitrary file which meets a certain condition by reading a specially crafted XML file.
